Image#1 is front camera view, Image#2 is merged UI frame.
Input Data:
- Driver Gaze Target (Ground Truth): irrelevant

Task:
Choose exactly one flag from each list below.
workzone_presence: {yes, no}
workzone_type: {none, lane closure, worker activity, merging zone, mixed, unclear}
traffic_condition: {free flow, following vehicle, dense traffic, intersection, traffic light, unclear}
primary_hazard: {none, worker, cone, vehicle, traffic light, mixed, unclear}
attention_alignment: {good, partial, poor}
risk_level: {low, medium, high}
recommended_action: {continue, slow down, prepare to stop, stop, prepare lane change}
Return ONLY valid JSON in one line, with no extra text and no markdown:
{"workzone_presence":"<one option>","workzone_type":"<one option>","traffic_condition":"<one option>","primary_hazard":"<one option>","attention_alignment":"<one option>","risk_level":"<one option>","recommended_action":"<one option>"}

